Introducing TrueWAP: A Volatility-Weighted Price Averaging Tool
code: twap <- TWAP(nikkei$OHLC, 50) vwap <- VWAP(nikkei$HLC3, nikkei$Volume, 50) true_wap <- TrueWAP(high = nikkei$High, low = nikkei$Low, close = nikkei$Close, true_range = nikkei$tr, period = 50)  twap_anchored <- anchoredTWAP(OHLC = nikkei$OHLC, period = nikkei$bars_since_segment) vwap_anchored <- anchoredVWAP(HLC3 = nikkei$HLC3, volume = nikkei$Volume, period = nikkei$bars_since_segment) true_wap_anchored <- anchoredTrueWAP(high = nikkei$High, low = nikkei$Low, close = nikkei$Close, true_range = nikkei$tr, period = nikkei$bars_since_segment)

title: Introducing TrueWAP: A Volatility-Weighted Price Averaging Tool
text: Overview: Calculated predetermined span (e.g., 50 bars), version continuously updates value using “contextual midpoint” derived previous close current bar’s high low. midpoint, referred True Range midpoint, ensures latest volatility fully incorporated averaged range-bound price. Interpretation: bar, rolling TrueWAP identifies upper boundary maximum previous close current high, lower boundary minimum previous close current low. average produces “contextual midpoint” weighted bar’s True Range (measure volatility). summing values fixed number bars (50, example) normalizing total True Range, indicator dynamically reflects price levels recent market volatility.

title: Introducing TrueWAP: A Volatility-Weighted Price Averaging Tool
text: Overview: version begins open first bar defined period, anchoring calculation point forward. Since previous data exist initial bar, high/low values serve baseline. subsequent bars, calculation uses previous close within period compute subsequent True Range values. method ensures measure reflects solely actual observed range period’s inception. Interpretation: anchored TrueWAP begins open defined period. first bar, due absence prior data, indicator uses simple average bar’s high low (hilo_mid) calculates range (High-Low). every subsequent bar, adopts “True Mid” True Range calculated using data previous close within period. differentiation ensures indicator remains solely reflective period’s actual price movements volatility.

title: Introducing TrueWAP: A Volatility-Weighted Price Averaging Tool
text: clarity, True Range determined maximum following: • current high minus current low, • absolute value current high minus previous close, • absolute value current low minus previous close. measure provides clear, objective assessment recent market volatility

title: Introducing TrueWAP: A Volatility-Weighted Price Averaging Tool
text: TrueWAP enhances traditional price averaging incorporating price levels volatility measures. reflecting central price (via contextual midpoint) scaling according fluctuations (True Range), TrueWAP offers traders analysts nuanced view market dynamics—especially volatile conditions—complementing tools focus solely time volume.
